# NotMatveevKondratyev_Libinotify

## Overview

Packages the `libinotify-kqueue` inotify implementation for Darwin and BSD, with a native Linux shim that preserves the same `libinotify` interface across platforms.

`NotMatveevKondratyev_Libinotify` builds the upstream `libinotify-kqueue`
sources (release 20240724) on Darwin and BSD, producing the standard
`libinotify` shared and static libraries plus `<sys/inotify.h>`. On Linux
it instead compiles a tiny Diskuv-authored compatibility library that
forwards the `inotify_*` calls to native Linux inotify syscalls, so
downstream packages see an identical `libinotify` surface on every
supported platform.

